task: How do I create a new project in Asana

steps.reasoning: Clicking this button will initiate the process of creating a new project, leading to the desired end state where the project name field is visible.
Clicking 'New project' will open the dialog where the user can enter the project name, moving towards the goal of creating a new project.
Clicking on 'Blank project' will initiate the creation of a new project, moving towards the goal of entering a project name.
The task is fully completed as the project name field is visible, allowing the user to enter a name for the new project.
